Carbon footprint info:
driving:
.12 kg per mile driven

food:
food in db

lights:
.1 kg per hour per room

hot water shower:
2.1 gallons per minute
.036kg per min shower

driving:
input (type in miles driven)
output input * .12 = kg of CO2 produced
store kg in db in driving column for the day

food:
carbon emissions
input (checklist for list of 7 foods in food.)
input number of portions of each food
query database for corresponding carbon weight for each food
multiply (weight * number of portions) if more than one portion
add up total weight
output total weight

lights:
input number of rooms
input hours of lights used
output (hours * rooms * .1)

hot water shower:
input minutes in shower:
output (input * .036)





